    h1 My Role
    hr

    h2 What I was responsible for
    p Recurly app, a robust recurring billing solution, felt dated at the aesthetic level. Myself and 3 other designers decided to create a new visual foundation to build upon. I worked on design visuals down to the nitty gritty details of implementation. I focused on identifying and establishing design patterns. Coordinating across teams to ensure consistency between design and implemented UI.

    h3 Planning & Scope Definition
    p I defined the product with my project manager partner. I evangelized customer goals and balanced business goals. I prioritized and negotiated features for launch and beyond.

    h3 Oversight & Coordination
    p I <em>designed across</em> and collaborated with the other designers to ensure consistency across both iOS and Android platforms by using a component-based design tool kit where possible.

    h3 Design Execution
    p I <em>designed down</em> on the web platform. I executed task flows, wireframes, prototypes, pattern libraries, and design specs.


