    h1 Challenges
    hr

    h2 Finding opportunities in obstacles

    h3 New front-end code
    p The client-side team decided to leverage Angular.js and React.js. This created excitement within the company, but raised questions for the design team. We knew we'd have to learn some of the technical constraints for us to work through.

    h3 API-dependent
    p The new app would be API-driven, taking advantage of Angular.js' abilities. This meant understand what is feasible and what was a stretch goal. We would need to design for the future, then scale it back to make it work now. What API endpoints weren't available would need to be built.

